<div class="homePagePanel2">
    <h2 class="homePageTestimony">What do people say about us?</h2>

    <div class="homePageAllPeople">

        <div class="homePagePeople1">
            <img class="homePage-luggage1-image" src="{{ 'homepage-luggage1.svg' | asset_url }}"/>
            <h3>ALBERT ONG</h3>
            <div class="homePageDescription">
                <p>Repaired my luggage with Tner and really happy with Thomas's workmanship.Highly recommended!</p>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="homePagePeople2" >
            <img class="homePage-luggage2-image" src="{{ 'homepage-luggage2.svg' | asset_url }}"/>
            <h3>PANG LI SHIN</h3>
            <div class="homePageDescription">
                <p>I was panicking for my last minute trip to Japan, feeling so unprepared. My friend recommended me 
                to rent a luggage with Tner and I realised that I can even buy disposable toothbrushes, one-time use 
                towels, make up remover capsules from them at the same time! If only the luggage can be delivered to me 
                for free, it would be 100% perfect.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="homePagePeople3">
            <img class="homePage-luggage3-image" src="{{ 'homepage-luggage3.svg' | asset_url }}"/>
            <h3>JENNY TAY</h3>
            <div class="homePageDescription">
                <p>Tner is an interesting concept that I stumbled upon when I was researching on buying a luggage.
                Never knew I can rent one! It was easy and fuss free, will rent again #supportlocal!</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>


